      <title>裕信银行称德国欺诈调查涉及一名前客户并涉及其他银行</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-says-german-fraud-probe-concerns-one-ex-client-involves-other-banks-2024-12-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit) 慕尼黑办事处周五遭到突击搜查，该银行表示，德国对涉嫌税务欺诈的调查涉及一位前客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-says-german-fraud-probe-concerns-one-ex-client-involves-other-banks-2024-12-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 13:25:49 GMT</pubDate>
