      <title>花旗集团提拔 344 名高管为董事总经理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-promotes-344-executives-managing-directors-2024-12-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团周四宣布，将 29 个国家的 344 名高管晋升为董事总经理，即 MD，这是该银行的高级职员头衔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-promotes-344-executives-managing-directors-2024-12-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 21:57:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
